    <div class="box-type-1">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Estilos do Painel</h2>
            <p>Define os estilos usados no painel.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="card-type-1">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <div class="card-icon">
